<div class="descr">October 14, 2011 posted by <i>Julio Merino</I></div><BR>

  <p>As the <a href="http://www.google-melange.com/gsoc/homepage/google/gsoc2011">Google Summer of Code 2011</a> (GSoC 2011) program concludes, we will be running a series of articles detailing the results of the projects mentored by The NetBSD Foundation.</p>

