            <h2><a href="http://blog.netbsd.org/tnf/entry/core_group_membership_change">Core group composition change</a></h2><BR>
<div class="descr">July 13, 2011 posted by <i>S.P.Zeidler</I></div><BR>

  The directors of the NetBSD Foundation and the Core group wish to
welcome Alan Barrett as new member of the Core group.

<p>He is replacing Antti Kantee; our sincerest thanks to Antti
for all his efforts during his core tenure, specially for pushing
through the tiered port support model and for making bug bounties
a reality.</p>


 [<a href="http://blog.netbsd.org/tnf/entry/core_group_membership_change#comment-form">0 comments</a>]

</p>


